title: SwiftTEA: Inside Scoop from the Tribeca Film Festival w/ @alibcook13
description:
Get the inside scoop from Taylor Swift's appearance at the Tribeca Film Festival from Alison, a Swiftie who was personally invited by Taylor Nation!

You are going to freak out when you hear who Alison sat next to!

Be sure to check out @alibcook13 on TikTok for great Swiftie content and for her incredible transitions! www.tiktok.com/@alibcook13

What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
